meta {
  name: Summarize Text (Direct)
  type: http
  seq: 9
}

post {
  url: {{base_url}}/text/summarize
  body: json
  auth: none
}

body:json {
  {
    "text": "This is a long text that needs to be summarized. It contains multiple sentences and paragraphs with important information that should be condensed into a brief summary. The text discusses various topics and provides detailed explanations that can be shortened while maintaining the key points and main ideas.",
    "max_length": 500
  }
}

assert {
  res.status: eq 200
  res.body.summary: isDefined
  res.body.original_length: isDefined
  res.body.summary_length: isDefined
}

docs {
  # Summarize Text (Direct)

  Riassume direttamente un testo senza bisogno di caricare un documento.
  Utile per riassunti rapidi di testo breve.

  ## Prerequisites
  - Ollama deve essere in esecuzione

  ## Request Body
  ```json
  {
    "text": "Your long text here...",    // Required: Testo da riassumere (min 10 char)
    "max_length": 500                    // Optional: Lunghezza massima riassunto (50-2000)
  }
  ```

  ## Response
  ```json
  {
    "summary": "This text discusses...",
    "original_length": 350,
    "summary_length": 85
  }
  ```

  ## Use Cases
  - Riassunto rapido di email
  - Condensare note
  - Estrazione concetti chiave
  - Preview contenuto

  ## Rate Limiting
  10 richieste per minuto
}
